<i>adjective</i>: 유익하다 [유ː이카다], 유리하다 [유ː리하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>유익하다 [유ː이카다]</dt><br>
<dd>profitable; advantageous</dd><br>
<dd>이롭거나 도움이 될 만하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being beneficial or helpful.</dd><br>
<dt>유리하다 [유ː리하다]</dt><br>
<dd>favorable; advantageous</dd><br>
<dd>이익이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having an advantage.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>